      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.16s">
        <div class="service-num">03</div>
        <span class="service-icon">🎨</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">Brand-Matched Design</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Your store will feel like it belongs to your brand — the right colours, fonts, imagery, and vibe to attract your exact customer.</p>
        <span class="service-arrow">↗</span>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal" style="transition-delay:0.08s">
        <div class="service-num">04</div>
        <span class="service-icon">📦</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">Product Setup</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">All your products uploaded, priced, described, and tagged properly. You don't have to touch a thing until you're selling.</p>
